description:
Cassandra Nix embarks on a journey with her friend Princess Donna to summon the ghost of five miners to fuck their brains out! Legend has it that if you go into the cave where these five miners died looking for Clementine, and sing "Oh my Darling Clementine" three times in a row the miners will emerge from the shadows and pound you senseless with their cocks.
Cassandra has no fear and takes on all five men at the same time! Rough sex, double penetration and more!
title: The Legend of Clementine Caves
